OL,7,FA summer camp leader who drugged
OL,8,Fchildren with sweets before sexually
OL,9,Fassaulting them has admitted drugging
OL,10,Fhis wife so she would not wake while
OL,11,Fthe abuse took place.
OL,13,FJon Ruben had previously admitted
OL,14,Fsexually assaulting two boys at a
OL,15,Fsummer camp at Stathern Lodge, in
OL,16,FStathern, Leicestershire, and child
OL,17,Fcruelty towards six other victims.
