OL,7,FRuben, who sobbed in the dock at
OL,8,FLeicester Crown Court during his plea
OL,9,Fhearing on Wednesday, admitted
OL,10,Fadministering a poison or noxious
OL,11,Fsubstance, Temazapam, to Susan Ruben
OL,12,Fbetween July 26 and 29 last year so
OL,13,Fshe would not wake up while he
OL,14,Fsexually assaulted the children.
OL,16,FThe 76-year-old defendant, who ran a
OL,17,Fholiday camp for at least 27 years,
OL,18,Fsaid "I'm so sorry" after entering his
OL,19,Fguilty plea.
