OL,7,FRuben, who sat in the dock wearing a
OL,8,Fblue shirt and beige trousers, laced
OL,9,Fsweets with tranquillising drugs and
OL,10,Fattacked two children after playing "a
OL,11,Fsweet game" with the youngsters.
OL,13,FIn November, he pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fsexual assault of a child under 13,
OL,15,Fassault of a child under 13 by
OL,16,Fpenetration, eight counts of child
OL,17,Fcruelty, three counts of making
OL,18,Findecent images of children and four
OL,19,Fdrugs charges.
