OL,7,FHe is due to be sentenced on Friday
OL,8,Ffor the offences.
OL,10,FJudge Timothy Spencer KC told Ruben
OL,11,Fhis sentencing will be a "very tough
OL,12,Fday in your life".
OL,14,FProsecutor Mary Prior KC told the
OL,15,Fcourt that Ruben asked police for a
OL,16,Fvoluntary interview when he admitted
OL,17,Fhe drugged his wife.
