OL,7,FRuben, of Wayte Court in Ruddington,
OL,8,FNottinghamshire, was arrested in July
OL,9,Flast year after a total of eight
OL,10,Fchildren were taken to hospital and
OL,11,Fliquid Xanax was found to have been
OL,12,Fused on some of the victims.
OL,14,FSeveral youngsters became ill after
OL,15,Fplaying the so-called sweet game and
OL,16,Ffound it difficult to walk, had
OL,17,Fslurred speech and could not wake up,
OL,18,FMs Prior previously told the court.
