OL,7,FChildren would often feel unwell the
OL,8,Fmorning after playing the "sweet
OL,9,Fgame", but Ruben would tell them they
OL,10,Fwere "overwrought".
OL,12,FThe court heard at a previous hearing
OL,13,Fthat the defendant's stepson raised
OL,14,Fconcerns with his partner during the
OL,15,Fcamp after finding baby oil, syringes
OL,16,Fwith white powder in and other items.
