OL,7,FThe owners and operators of Stathern
OL,8,FLodge are independent from those who
OL,9,Fuse or hire the lodge were "not
OL,10,Fconnected to the incident",
OL,11,FLeicestershire Police have said.
OL,13,FThe indecent images charges admitted
OL,14,Fby Ruben related to 50 category A
OL,15,Findecent videos of children, 22
OL,16,FCategory B videos and seven Category C
OL,17,Fvideos made between August 2023 and
OL,18,FJune last year.
OL,20,FNone of the images concerned relate to
OL,21,Fchildren who were at the summer camp.
